title: 2009 European Athletics U23 Championships – Men's 5000 metres
text:
The men's <a href="5000%20metres">5000 metres</a> event at the <a href="2009%20European%20Athletics%20U23%20Championships">2009 European Athletics U23 Championships</a> was held in <a href="Kaunas">Kaunas</a>, Lithuania, at <a href="Darius%20and%20Gir%C4%97nas%20Stadium">S. Dariaus ir S. Girėno stadionas (Darius and Girėnas Stadium)</a> on 16 July.
Results.
Final.
16 July
Participation.
According to an unofficial count, 20 athletes from 12 countries participated in the event.
